about.title: Acerca de
about.description: Symbiota Docs - actual es un repositorio central de documentación sobre portales de datos basados en Symbiota. Este sitio es mantenido por Symbiota Support Hub, pero se alienta a todos los usuarios de Symbiota a contribuir. Contáctenos para contribuir o proporcionar comentarios sobre este sitio.

New Feature.title: New Feature
New Feature.description: v1.3 has this new feature detailed herein. Yay!

User Guide/Accessibility.title: Accessibility Options
User Guide/Accessibility.description: Users who create accounts in the portal can adjust Accessibility Preferences, which are designed to improve accessibility to the site for people with disabilities. More information about accessibility as defined by U.S. Section 508 can be found here.
